CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 13, 1952, pg. 27 reads: "Golfdom's Best - Being average wasn't good enough at the South Park golf course last week as the above champions proved in annexing UGA crowns.  On the left is Ted Rhodes who successfully defended his professional title with 280...- Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of golfer Ted Rhodes, swinging golf club on South Park golf course for UGA tournament
